{"title":"长沙吟","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长沙吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在岳麓山下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着湘江凝望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一朵浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎都在欢唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江的水呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么激昂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是当年起义农民的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还沸腾在你的胸膛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江的水呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么喧腾？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是当年革命先烈的正气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在你的内心激荡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江的水呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么闪光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是因为最明亮的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就诞生在你的身旁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在岳麓山下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着湘江凝望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一朵浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在我的心头开放……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"橘子洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在橘子洲头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那橘林悠游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采摘一枚青橘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠给远方朋友……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友，这枚青橘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要珍爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为是湘江的江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它辛勤地灌溉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友，这枚青橘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要珍贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在生长它的橘树侧畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾倒下过革命先烈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友，这枚青橘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要珍藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它永远会散发着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命发源地的清香！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采下一枚青橘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠给远方朋友；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又把我几行诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在橘树枝头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长沙第一师范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那湘江侧畔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行人走过常常留步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻舟飘过常常停帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多白发老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多海外贵宾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也常常轻轻推开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校的门扇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席伏过的课桌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席翻过的书卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使多少人的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起壮阔的波澜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席沐浴的水井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席散步的校园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使多少人的肺腑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充溢生活的甘甜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在这里凝思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像回到童年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真想再从头学起啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这座学校里面。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}